{
  "text": "Nevertheless, whereas A\u03b4-LEP have been studied in DOC patients [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , the assessment of C-fiber LEP (C-LEP) has not been yet performed in DOC individuals. C-LEP have been shown to be generated by C-fiber activation through laser stimuli with specific characteristics, but they probably share common cortical generators with A\u03b4-LEP [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
